sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Insight as Insight Box
    participant Tooltip as SelectionTooltip
    participant Sidebar as Sidebar
    participant API as graph_search_api

    User->>Insight: Select text in reasoning
    Insight-->>Tooltip: mouseup in .insight-box
    Note over Tooltip: Floating popup appears<br/>Selected: [text]<br/>Input: Analyze [text] in more detail

    alt Ask
        User->>Tooltip: Click Ask / press Enter
        Tooltip->>Sidebar: onSearch(query)
        Sidebar->>API: POST /api/nl-search-enriched-stream
        Note over API: Full AI Search flow runs
        API-->>Sidebar: SSE stream → new results
    else Cancel
        User->>Tooltip: Click Cancel / press Escape
        Tooltip->>Tooltip: Hide
    end
